text: Jeremy Harry Bird (born 14 September 1989) is a British sport shooter. He participated at the 2019 World Shotgun Championships, where he won skeet bronze. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1989 births Category:British male sport shooters Category:Skeet shooters Category:European Games competitors for Great Britain Category:Shooters at the 2019 European Games
